# BizPal CRM
A Simple CRM for Small Businesses

## Overview
BizPal CRM is a lightweight Customer Relationship Management system designed to help small businesses track customers and leads efficiently. 
Core features include:
- Add customer
- Update status
- Notes
- Dashboard

This repository contains the **frontend code** for the project.

## Project Tracks
The project is developed collaboratively across multiple tracks:
- Frontend Development (this repo)
- Backend Development
- UI/UX Design
- Product Management
- Product Design
- Technical Writing

Each track is responsible for presenting their contributions during the final capstone presentation.